li></ul> <hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/> <h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Still Curious?</strong></h2> <p>If you are like us, who likes to analyse a little more or check out content in different formats, well you are in luck. Below you can find some suitable content we found.</p> <p><a href="https://blog.thealtinvestor.in/earn-upto-12-returns-on-insurance-policies-thepolicyexchange-platform-review?utm_source=hashnode_blog_newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=earn-upto-12-returns-on-insurance-policies-thepolicyexchange-platform-review" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">ALT Investor &#8211; Can You Earn Upto 12% Returns On Insurance Policies? (Blog)</a></p> <p><a href="https://youtu.be/qrhujKGniVg?si=ki6N0hpN7erYuyRP" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">ALT Investor &#8211; Can you earn 14% return by investing in Insurance policies? (YT Podcast)</a></p> <p><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/neil-borate-1a435a57_people-who-want-to-surrender-their-life-insurance-activity-7321345196258942976-O1Tz?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=member_android&amp;rcm=ACoAAAFsxBYBSrjQsQjRazrR4ZEdx8z_udFpfBk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Neil Borate &#8211; How you can earn up to 15% returns from old life insurance policies (LinkedIn)</a></p> <p>Note:&nbsp;We don’t have any affiliation&nbsp;with them. We are sharing links only for educational purposes. The opinions expressed by them belong solely to them and do not reflect the views of Vrid.</p> <p></p> """,
